=head1 NAME
.PP
Datetime::Hash - Fast XS-based date formatting into hashes using ICU.
.PP
=head1 SYNOPSIS
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
use Datetime::Hash qw(format_datetime format_legacy);

# Modern Schema
my $hash = format_datetime(\[dq]2025-12-17 13:15:00\[dq], \[dq]Europe/Berlin\[dq], \[dq]de_DE\[dq]);

# Legacy Schema (Compatible with 0.0.x)
my $old = format_legacy(\[dq]2025-12-17 13:15:00\[dq], \[dq]Europe/Berlin\[dq]);
\f[R]
.fi
.PP
=head1 DESCRIPTION
.PP
Utilizes the ICU (International Components for Unicode) library to
perform high-speed date formatting directly in C.
.PP
